quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  46,21,"Janto fii musiЙ—Й“e Aadi (Huudi) Й“en, nde o jertinirnoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en aynde nden - gomЙ—ii hari jertinooji yawtiino yeeso makko e Й“aawo makko - wonnde: \"Wata on rewu si wanaa Allah. Min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Гұalaande mawnde"
  46,22,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"E a aru men fii yo a firliaa men e rewetee- Й—i amen Й—in? Awa addan men ko kammbiranЙ—aa men kon, si wonii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  46,23,"O maaki: \"Ganndal ngal ko ka Allah woni. Min mi yottinanay on tun woni, ko mi nulaa kon. Ko woni tun mi yi'ii ko on yimЙ“e majjaaЙ“e"
  46,24,"Nde Й“e yi'unoo ruulde honde weeЙ“itii fewtiri ayЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e wi'i: \"Ndee ko duulere toЙ“aynde e men\". Ko nden kan woni ! ko hawjirnoЙ—on kon : ko henndu, ndu lepte muusuЙ—e woni e mun"
  46,25,"hindu muncira kala huunde, yamiroore Joomi mayru\". ЖҒe waЙ—tini, tawi yi'etaake si wanaa koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“itirta yimЙ“e bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  46,26,"GomЙ—ii Men yeЙ—iino Й“e, e kon ko Men yeЙ—aali on e mun. Men waЙ—ani Й“e nanЙ—e, e giiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e. Kono Й—en nanЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, e giiЙ—e maЙ“Й“e e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e (fow) duncanaali Й“e goЙ—Й—um, tawde Й“e laatino yeddooЙ“e Aayeeje Allah Й—en. Ko Й“e jalkitaynoo kon jippii e maЙ“Й“e"
  46,27,"GomЙ—ii Men halkiino ca'e wonunooЙ“e sera mon; Men firlitiri Aayeeje Й—en, belajo'o Й“e ruttoto"
  46,28,"Ko haЙ—no Й—in Й—i Й“e jogitornoo reweteeЙ—i Й“aЙ—tinorЙ—i gaanin Allah, faaboo Й“e? Tigi on, Й—in majjirii Й“e; ko Й—um wonunoo fenaande maЙ“Й“e e ko Й“e fefindotonoo"
  46,29,"Janto tuma nde Men imminnoo fedde jinna e maaЙ—a, hiЙ—i heЙ—oo Alqur'aana. Nde Й—i tawanoo Й—um, Й—i wi'i: \"HeЙ—ee\"...Nde [janngin kin] timmunoo, Й—i huccitiri ka yimЙ“e majji, jeertinooji"
  46,30,"ЖҠi wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu amen, men nanii Deftere jippinaande Й“aawo Muusaa, goonginnde Й—en adiiЙ—e nde. Hinde fewna e goonga e laawol focciingol"
  46,31,"Ko ono yo mbatu amen, nootee noddoowo e Allah on, gomЙ—inon mo. [Ontuma] O haforanay on junuubimon Й—in, O daЙ—nda on lepte muusuЙ—e"
  46,32,"Kala mo nootaake noddoowo e Allah on, o wonaa laawotooЙ—o ka leydi, o alaa kadi giЙ—o gaanin Makko. Ko Й“en woni e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  46,33,"E Й“ee yi'aali wonnde ko Allah tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, O ronkiraali tagugol Й—i, wonnde ko O haЙ—tanЙ—o wuurnitugol maayЙ“e Й“en? Ko non woniri. Pellet, ko O haЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde"
  46,34,"Г‘alnde heeferЙ“e Й“en weeЙ“itoytee e Yiite ngen, [Й“e wi'anee]: \"Wanaa goonga nii?\" ЖҒe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri! Men woondirii Joomi amen!\". O Daala : \"Awa meeЙ—iree non lepte Й—en, sabu kon ko yeddiraynoЙ—on"
  46,35,"MuГұГұor muГұal joomiraaЙ“e pellital Й“en ka NulaaЙ“e; wata a hawjan Й“e. Г‘alnde Й“e yi'oyta ko Й“e kammbiranaa kon, Й“e wa'oyay wa si Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano [ka leydi] si wanaa dumunna-hun Гұalorma. ЖҠun ko yottinal. Ko homЙ“e halketee si wanaa yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  47,1,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e Й“e falii laawol Allah ngol, O bonnii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,2,"GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“e gomЙ—ini ko jippinaa kon e Muhammad - on goonga immorЙ—o e Joomi maЙ“Й“e - O yawtanii Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O moЖҙЖҙinii fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on"
  47,3,"Ko waЙ—i Й—um, ko tawde yedduЙ“e Й“en jokkii meere nden, gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en kan jokki goonga kan immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e on. Ko wano nii Allah piyiranta yimЙ“e Й“en mise maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,4,"Si on arii hawrude e yedduЙ“e Й“en (ka hare), ko soppugol daaЙ—e Й—en. Haa si on Й—uЙ—Й—inii warugol Й“e, haЙ“Й“on koyЙ—e Й—en. Ko si on moЖҙЖҙoray e maЙ“Й“e accitugol Й“e Й“aawo Й—um, maa si ko soktiigu, haa hare nden wallina jogaaji mayre. Ko non Гұaawiraa, si Allah no muuyunoo, O wallitotono on e maЙ“Й“e, ko woni tun, ko no O jarribora yoga mon e dow yoga. WaraaЙ“e fii Allah Й“en, pellet, O yeebataa golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,5,"Arma O fewna Й“e, O moЖҙЖҙina fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e"
  47,6,"O naadoya Й“e Aljanna, mo O anndini Й“e fii mun"
  47,7,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on wonii wallooЙ“e fii Allah, O wallay on, O tabintina teppe mon Й—en"
  47,8,"YedduЙ“e Й“ee kan, halkaare woodanii Й“e, O majjinii kadi golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"
  47,9,"ЖҠum le ko tawde Й“e aГұii ko Allah jippini kon, O bonni golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en"